Class ArrayIntList

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.Integer>, java.util.Collection<java.lang.Integer>, java.util.List<java.lang.Integer>, IntCollection, PrimitiveCollection<java.lang.Integer>, IntIterable, IntList, PrimitiveList<java.lang.Integer>, PrimitiveCollectable<java.lang.Integer>

    public class ArrayIntList
extends AbstractIntList
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    Array based implementation of IntList for primitive int elements.

    This class implements List allowing seamless integration with other APIs.

    Add, Remove, Set and Clear are supported.

    Since:
    1.0
